{"type":null,"faqId":19970,"title":"如何添加邮件附件，对附件的大小限制是多少？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>在邮件编辑界面，点击 “</span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.11.2.1.1.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.4.11.2.1.1.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=66701\" style=\"width:0.25in;height:0.18472221in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>” 可添加附件。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>使用 HUAWEI MediaPad T1 8.0 Pro 发送邮件，单个附件的大小不得超过5MB。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.4.11.2.3\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=66702\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果一封邮件的附件大小超过5M，那么这封邮件的发送成功率会变低，这是由不同邮箱服务器的限制所致。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":168,"faqType":"信息与电子邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3391","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Messaging-Emailing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1425286523000,"seriesProductName":"T1-821w,T1-823L","visitedTimes":15,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"邮件附件,添加附件,附件大小,邮件大小、限制","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}